===Noun===
'''[[toss]]-[[up]]'''
#{{idiom}} A [[decision]] in which neither choice is clearly [[favorable]] or [[unfavorable]], or for which the [[outcome]] does not matter.
#:''It's really a '''toss-up''' between the red skirt with blue stripes and the blue skirt with red stripes.  They both look good and fit well.''
#Either of two [[outcome]]s that are [[equally]] [[likely]].
#The [[toss]] of a [[coin]] used to [[decide]] some [[issue]].

